des:
This skill is a part of Mini Games.

Become the ultimate workout warrior in this game of silly workout moves. Our drill sergeant will put you through your paces and get you doing silly animal impressions.

Make sure your crab-scurrying, salmon jumping and ninja kicking skills are on point. Copy the instructions and have a laugh!

Top tip: Try to remember all the instructions you have been given. You may get a question to unlock bonus coins.

This skill is supported on all Alexa enabled devices, and has awesome visuals and animations for devices with screens, as well as immersive audio.

This skill is part of Mini Games.

If you launch this skill, it will tell you to open Mini Games.
